OL,2,MPhones for the Deaf
OL,4,CMisha
OL,5,CSun 13:10-13:40
OL,6,CStage C
OL,8,GHave you ever gotten a call from a
OL,9,Grelay operator who wants to connect
OL,10,Gyou with someone who's using a text
OL,11,Gphone? Did you hang up? Stop it! I
OL,12,Gwant to tell you about the past,
OL,13,Gpresent, and future of textphones, and
OL,14,Ghow deaf people and people with
OL,15,Gdifficulty speaking communicate with
OL,16,Gphone users. Finally, I want you to
OL,17,Gstop hanging up on me! Let's look at
OL,18,Gthe systems behind different assistive
OL,19,Gtechnologies, how they are used, and
OL,20,Gthe people who keep them running-
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
